{"tid":2394189,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人民銳評：「封區檢測」是香港經濟文明之恥","createTime":"2021-02-04T04:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T09:48:07.000Z","uid":250654,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"83bdbc31941f0cfd99b2b2bebf0bcc0b87d39cde","tid":2394189,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:16:14.000Z","msg":"「封鎖社區檢測」本不值一駁，更無任何發展壯大的可能。<strong><span class=\"red\">但「封區檢測」有毒，剝奪市民消費選擇的自由</span></strong>，損傷市民經營活動的自由，在商界刮起「黑色恐怖」之風，就不得不予以鞭撻了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人家正在用餐，他們進來搗亂，把市民嚇走；人家正在營業，他們拉上封條，把設施封鎖；市民的衣食住行均要考慮他們的好惡和臉色，<strong><span class=\"red\">這還是一個自由經濟體應有的現象嗎</span></strong>，這還是一個國際大都市應該呈現的文明嗎？不，<strong>「封區檢測」只是幌子，只是排除異己的手段；</strong><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">香港政府想要的只是「攬炒」</span></span></strong>，是香港經濟的衰敗、社會文明的崩塌、法治精神的潰敗。<br />\n他們以「香港警察」和黑社會的做派推銷「封鎖社區檢測」，是對社區二字的褻瀆、對基本人權的踐踏，野蠻、粗暴，充滿了反社會、反文明的意味。<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n用字係咪似曾相識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500acf8fc4bd411c35c86e8f8b83b7e2900dd513","tid":2394189,"uid":250654,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMe0BdL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMe0BdL.gif&h=646dc4fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26388711ff08a16f2deacc5fcf2ba0753292a80d","tid":2394189,"uid":250654,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"再俾多D貼士大家諗下出處<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBWdbun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBWdbun.jpg&h=4923929b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f7992bab82bc3a8463d5375f425a7e125f3e359","tid":2394189,"uid":250654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"封區檢測注定失敗<img src=\"/assets/